This section demonstrates visualising model diagnostic and model parameters by using parameters package.





Toyota Corolla case study will be used. The purpose of study is to build a model to discover factors affecting prices of used-cars by taking into consideration a set of explanatory variables.










In the code chunk below, read_xls() of readxl package is used to import the data worksheet of ToyotaCorolla.xls workbook into R.
zjq car_resale &lt;- read_xls("data/ToyotaCorolla.xls",                         "data") car_resale}



zjq ExpCatStat(car_resale,            Target = "Price",            result = "Stat")}

